<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">一想起在這島上發生的事情，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就忍不住感傷起來。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣真是<delay8 />一點都不像我啊，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很快就要跟這座島告別啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />在你們心裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />應該已經牢牢記住<delay8 />
曾有個叫做<tag a="110" b="10" />的男人了吧！
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不管你們對我的印象是好是壞都一樣啦，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～哈哈！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我預計明天會打包行李，<delay8 />
後天就要離開島上了。<10_4 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />行程排得很緊湊對吧？
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay8 />一想到新的島上，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有冒險、<delay20 />浪漫，<delay20 />跟邂逅在等著我，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就興奮得不得了啊！！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
